---
title: 请求日志中间件流程
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 客户端
    participant ASGI as ASGI Server (uvicorn)
    participant RLM as RequestLogMiddleware
    participant Config as log_config_cache
    participant Next as 下一个中间件/路由
    participant DB as MySQL (request_logs)

    Client->>ASGI: HTTP Request
    ASGI->>RLM: __call__(scope, receive, send)

    Note over RLM: === 1. 判断是否记录 ===
    RLM->>RLM: 检查 scope['type'] == 'http'
    RLM->>Config: should_log(method, path)
    Config-->>RLM: true/false

    alt 不需要记录
        RLM->>Next: 直接透传
        Next-->>RLM: 响应
        RLM-->>ASGI: 返回响应
    end

    Note over RLM: === 2. 收集请求体 ===
    RLM->>RLM: 包装 receive 函数
    RLM->>Next: await self.app(scope, wrapped_receive, wrapped_send)
    Next->>Next: 处理请求
    Next-->>RLM: 请求体 chunks 已收集

    Note over RLM: === 3. 收集响应体 ===
    RLM->>RLM: 包装 send 函数
    RLM->>RLM: 捕获 http.response.body
    RLM->>RLM: 仅收集 JSON Content-Type 响应

    Note over RLM: === 4. 敏感信息脱敏 ===
    RLM->>RLM: _process_json_payload(request_body)
    Note over RLM: 12个敏感字段替换为 ***:
    Note over RLM: password, token, secret, hash_ps,
    Note over RLM: authorization, access_token, refresh_token,
    Note over RLM: api_key, private_key, credential,
    Note over RLM: cookie, set-cookie

    Note over RLM: === 5. 操作者识别 ===
    RLM->>RLM: _get_operator_info(scope)
    Note over RLM: 从 Cookie access_token 或
    Note over RLM: Authorization header 解码 JWT
    RLM->>RLM: 提取 operator_id, account, username

    Note over RLM: === 6. 异步持久化 ===
    RLM->>RLM: 计算 duration_ms
    RLM->>DB: INSERT INTO request_logs
    Note over DB: method, path, full_url, status_code,
    Note over DB: success, duration_ms, operator_*,
    Note over DB: ip, user_agent, request_query,
    Note over DB: request_body, response_body, error_message

    alt 写入失败
        DB-->>RLM: 异常
        RLM->>RLM: db.rollback()
        Note over RLM: 不影响业务响应
    else 写入成功
        DB-->>RLM: 提交成功
    end

    RLM-->>ASGI: 返回响应给客户端
